OL,6,FA dance teacher who helped save the
OL,7,Flives of children caught up in the
OL,8,FSouthport stabbings including locking
OL,9,Fone in a toilet has described the
OL,10,F"terrifying" moment the attacker
OL,11,Fbanged on the door in an attempted to
OL,12,Fget in.
OL,14,FA public inquiry at Liverpool Town
OL,15,FHall aims to examine Axel Rudakubana's
OL,16,Fdealings with relevant agencies before
OL,17,Fhe carried out his violent attack.
