OL,3,CSouthport dance teacher who protected
OL,4,Cgirls 'still haunted by screams'
OL,6,FThree girls - Alice da Silva Aguiar,
OL,7,Fnine, Bebe King, six, and Elsie Dot
OL,8,FStancombe, seven - were murdered in
OL,9,Fthe incident on 29 July 2024, with the
OL,10,Fattacker attempting to murder 10
OL,11,Fothers.
OL,13,FHeidi Liddle, who had been asked to be
OL,14,Fa guest dance teacher at the event,
OL,15,Ftold the inquiry that she is still
OL,16,F"haunted by screams" after a knifeman
OL,17,Fentered The Hart Centre while she was
OL,18,Fmaking bracelets with the children.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
