OL,4,Cgirls 'still haunted by screams'
OL,6,FThe mother, who had just returned from
OL,7,Fmaternity leave, told the hearing on
OL,8,FWednesday, 10 September, that the room
OL,9,F"filled with joy and happiness"
OL,10,Fchanged "dramatically and
OL,11,Fdevastatingly within seconds."
OL,13,F"Suddenly I saw my friend and
OL,14,Fcolleague being brutally attacked,"
OL,15,Fshe recalled. "I couldn't process what
OL,16,Fwas happening. Everything happened so
OL,17,Fquickly, it was just a matter of
OL,18,Fseconds.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
