OL,3,CSouthport dance teacher who protected
OL,4,Cgirls 'still haunted by screams'
OL,6,F"At that moment, there was no time to
OL,7,Fthink but to just run and usher as
OL,8,Fmany children away from danger as
OL,9,Fpossible.
OL,11,F"The children were running towards the
OL,12,Fstairwell, when I noticed one of the
OL,13,Fgirls running in the opposite
OL,14,Fdirection towards the toilet.
OL,16,F"I saw a flash of green and I pushed
OL,17,Fher inside and locked the door,
OL,18,Freassuring her and telling her to be
OL,19,Fquiet."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
