OL,6,FHeidi was in tears when she told the
OL,7,Fhearing that whilst in the toilet, the
OL,8,Fperpetrator was banging and rattling
OL,9,Fthe door attempting to get in ` only
OL,10,Fstopping when the police arrived.
OL,12,F"The girls' screaming and fearing for
OL,13,Four lives haunts me to this day," she
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FThe dancer teacher said the guilt she
OL,17,Fbears is "crushing" and she is
OL,18,Fconstantly replaying what happened
OL,19,F"over and over in my mind, what I was
OL,20,Fable to do, what else could I have
OL,21,Fdone, the what ifs."
