OL,3,CSouthport dance teacher who protected
OL,4,Cgirls 'still haunted by screams'
OL,6,F"I felt that this understated the huge
OL,7,Fmental trauma and suffering
OL,8,Fexperienced by us all and which we
OL,9,Fcontinue to do so. I felt my feelings
OL,10,Fwere diminished and that I shouldn't
OL,11,Ffeel the way I did and continue to do."
OL,13,FHeidi told the inquiry of the daily
OL,14,Fflashbacks she experiences, and how
OL,15,Fshe "sees" the attacker at various
OL,16,Fpoints in the day. She said: "I've
OL,17,Fcome to realise that this is just how
OL,18,Fmy life is now."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
