OL,6,FHeidi went on to say that she wants to
OL,7,Fhelp and support the charities in the
OL,8,Fname of the three "beautiful" girls
OL,9,Fwho lost their lives but believes she
OL,10,Fcould be a trigger and "the last thing
OL,11,FI want is to add to their trauma."
OL,13,FShe hopes the inquiry, expected to
OL,14,Flast until November, will ensure that
OL,15,Fno-one should ever "have to go through
OL,16,Fthe life-changing devastation that
OL,17,Fthis evil individual was able to
OL,18,Finflict on us that day."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
